        "content": "## Scenarios de validation\n\n### Test 1: baseline\n- pingall\n- h1 ping -c 3 h4\n- h4 iperf -c 10.0.0.1 -u -p 5001 -b 10M -t 10\n- link s1 s3 down\n- h2 ping -c 3 h3\n- link s1 s3 up\n\n### Test 2: firewall h1-h4 + QoS h1-h3\n- h1 ping -c 2 h4\n- h2 ping -c 2 h4\n- h1 iperf -c 10.0.0.3 -u -p 5001 -b 50M -t 10\n- link s1 s3 down\n- h2 ping -c 2 h4\n- link s1 s3 up\n\n### Test 3: firewall h2-h3 + QoS h4-h1\n- h2 ping -c 2 h3\n- h1 ping -c 2 h3\n- h4 iperf -c 10.0.0.1 -u -p 5001 -b 10M -t 10\n- link s1 s4 down\n- h1 ping -c 2 h4\n- link s1 s4 up",
